text: Julius Carl Fritz Manteuffel was a gymnast from Germany. Julius competed at the 1896 Summer Olympics and at the 1990 Summer Olympics. He was born on 11 January 1875 and died on 21 April 1941.Fritz Manteuffel == References == Category:1875 births Category:1941 deaths Category:German gymnasts Category:Olympic gold medalists for Germany Category:Sportspeople from Berlin
